::KitKat::

She saw the shots hit the ground and hit around her.
"SLAG!"
She jumped side to side dodging the bullets.  One shot hit her in the arm. 
"OUCH"
She got behind a rock and pulled out her gun.
"Hey you two, grab some cover quick." she yelled at Quickstrike and 
Stringtra.  She returned fire at the bot in the air. Her arm leaked mech 
fliud from the wound, but it was a glancing blow from the bullet, and the 
damage was minimal. She kept firing on the bot in the air.

::Magmatron::

    He heard the message from Bobertron. "Mantella, now we have a real
situation, lock onto Bobertron's cairdinates, we have a fight. Shredder you 
help also. I'm on my way."
He transformed into Beast Mode and flew to the battle, he saw Bobertron
attacking. He knew who were emimies. He transformed into Robot Mode and
attacked. His jets caught him just in time and he hovered there pumping out 
shot after shot.
